fields.name: notification_template
fields.text:
Dear {{ user.name }}

This message is to inform you that on {{ email_sent_datetime }} {{ num_messages }} email{% if num_messages > 1 %}s{% endif %} were sent resulting from the execution of the action with name "{{ action.name }}".

{% if filter_present %}

The action had a filter that reduced the number of messages from {{ num_rows }} to {{ num_selected }}.

{% else %}

All the data rows stored in the workflow table were used.

{% endif %} Regards. The OnTask Support Team

fields.name: Scenario 4
fields.description_text: Send an email to each of the students in a program with different explanations of why the course is relevant for their degree.

fields.description_text: Message to those students in SMED
fields.content:
Hello {{ GivenName }}

Welcome to the course. As you may know, there are several techniques and concepts in SMED that are relevant to this course. For example one of them is ....


Regards.

Sarah Johnson

Course Coordinator
